milestones.description: Aminul Islam has become the top scorer for BAN in ODIs with 108 runs, going past Minhajul Abedin's 107
Gholam Nousher has become the top wicket-taker for BAN in ODIs with 4 wickets, going past Azhar Hossain's 3
Aminul Islam and Enamul Haque's 48-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Jahangir Shah and Akram Khan
Azhar Hossain has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for BAN, going past Raqibul Hasan's 1
Gazi Ashraf has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for BAN, going past Gholam Nousher
